OL,3,CRobust discussions expected over
OL,4,Cproposed Stormont budget
OL,6,FThe Stormont Executive is expected to
OL,7,Fdiscuss this year's budget on
OL,8,FThursday, following the re-
OL,9,Festablishment of devolved government
OL,10,Fat the end of January.
OL,12,FHowever, the Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,13,FArchibald is expecting talks to be
OL,14,Frobust as departments argue for more
OL,15,Fmoney.
OL,17,FLast week, she said she has received
OL,18,Fresource bids from ministers for
OL,19,Fpublic services that are more than
OL,20,Fthree times the available budget.
