OL,6,F"There's an early sense I've got that
OL,7,Fthere are some critical issues across
OL,8,Fthe education sector ... the more back
OL,9,Foffice. I think they haven't had the
OL,10,Flevel of investment they should have
OL,11,Fhad in recent years, and I think
OL,12,Funless we're careful, that will start
OL,13,Fto appear in the front line, some real
OL,14,Fcracks ... things like levels of
OL,15,Fdigital investment, IT security."
OL,17,FAsked about ring-fencing funding for
OL,18,Fschools, Mr Pengelly painted what he
OL,19,Ftermed a "brutal reality".
