OL,6,F"So the brutal reality is we're not
OL,7,Fgoing to get the funding settlement
OL,8,Fthat we want or indeed we need in
OL,9,Fterms of service provision, so the way
OL,10,Fforward is going to land on some
OL,11,Freally hard-nose choices and I think
OL,12,Fthe best thing that we can do with
OL,13,Fschools is be honest that we're not
OL,14,Fgoing to have a financial settlement
OL,15,Fthat solves the problem but that what
OL,16,Fwe are prepared to do is have
OL,17,Fconversations about prioritisation.
OL,19,F"That's going to need to happen across
OL,20,Fthis sector and across every sector.
