OL,6,F"I think we need to prioritise and
OL,7,Flook at areas where need is most acute
OL,8,Fand establish some real sense of
OL,9,Fprioritisation.
OL,11,F"I genuinely hope that that will be a
OL,12,Fsort of hunkering down for a year or
OL,13,Ftwo and that the dial will start to
OL,14,Fturn in terms of the financial
OL,15,Fposition, but I genuinely worry that,
OL,16,Fin terms of many services, we're
OL,17,Frapidly approaching the point at which
OL,18,Fthey become unsustainable.
OL,20,F"So it's about trying to maintain the
OL,21,Fservices through that."
