OL,6,FThe former Department of Justice
OL,7,FPermanent Secretary said while he had
OL,8,Fheard "a fair bit of negative noise"
OL,9,Fabout the EA before taking up the
OL,10,Fpost, he said he has found "the
OL,11,Fdiametric opposite of what I've
OL,12,Fencountered in a week and a half in
OL,13,Fthe organisation".
OL,15,F"It's an organisation full of energy,
OL,16,Ffull of enthusiasm, and frankly, full
OL,17,Fof inspirational people who are trying
OL,18,Fto do their very best," he said.
OL,20,F"The role I want to do is very firmly
OL,21,Fstand behind them and support them."
